Hypno Integration Requirements

Becoming Protocol --- Audio Conditioning Layer

Version 1.0 --- January 2026

Executive Summary

This document defines requirements for integrating hypnosis audio
content into the Becoming Protocol system. The integration creates a
structured conditioning layer that pairs with existing arousal state
tracking, denial management, and feminization practice to deepen
identity reinforcement through audio-based trance work.

The system manages two primary content categories: **feminization
hypno** (Bambi series for identity work) and **FLR/obedience hypno**
(Elswyth series for goddess worship, chastity conditioning, and denial
reinforcement). Content recommendations are dynamically generated based
on denial day, arousal state, time of day, and protocol phase.

Part 1: Content Library Architecture

1.1 Content Categories

The system organizes hypno content into functional categories that serve
different psychological purposes:

  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Category**       **Primary Creator** **Purpose**
  ------------------ ------------------- -----------------------------------
  Feminization       Bambi Sleep         Identity conditioning, feminine
                                         self-concept reinforcement, service
                                         to Goddess framing

  Chastity           Elswyth             Denial reinforcement, chastity
                                         conditioning, orgasm control
                                         mantras

  Goddess Worship    Elswyth             FLR framing, service orientation,
                                         worship ritual establishment

  Sleep/Relaxation   Elswyth, Nimja      Overnight conditioning, dream
                                         integration, gentle reinforcement

  Deep Trance        Various             Extended absorption sessions,
                                         goon-mode integration, advanced
                                         conditioning
  --------------------------------------------------------------------------

1.2 Database Schema

New tables required for hypno content management:

\-- Hypno content library

CREATE TABLE hypno_content (

id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),

name VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL,

creator VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,

series VARCHAR(100),

category VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,

\-- Categories: feminization, chastity, goddess_worship,

\-- sleep, deep_trance, identity, obedience

duration_minutes INT,

intensity VARCHAR(20), \-- gentle, moderate, intense

tier INT DEFAULT 1, \-- 1-4 unlock tiers

best_for_denial_range INT\[\], \-- \[min_day, max_day\]

best_for_arousal_states VARCHAR(50)\[\],

best_time_of_day VARCHAR(20)\[\], \-- morning, afternoon, evening, night

requires_cage BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,

pairs_with_edging BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,

external_url TEXT,

notes TEXT,

created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW()

);

\-- User listening history

CREATE TABLE hypno_sessions (

id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),

user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users(id),

content_id UUID REFERENCES hypno_content(id),

started_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW(),

completed BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,

duration_listened_minutes INT,

denial_day_at_listen INT,

arousal_state_at_listen VARCHAR(50),

was_caged BOOLEAN,

paired_with_edge_session UUID,

effectiveness_rating INT, \-- 1-5 self-report

notes TEXT

);

Part 2: Recommendation Engine

2.1 State-Based Content Selection

Content recommendations are generated based on the user\'s current state
across multiple dimensions:

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Denial Day**    **Content Focus**       **Rationale**
  ----------------- ----------------------- -----------------------------
  Day 0-2 (Reset)   Chastity conditioning,  Low arousal = receptive to
                    sleep hypno, obedience  obedience framing without
                                            sexual distraction

  Day 3-5           Bambi identity + denial Arousal returning; pair
  (Building)        reinforcement           feminization with wanting

  Day 6-10 (Sweet   Full Bambi sessions,    Peak receptivity; strongest
  Spot)             edge session content    conditioning window

  Day 11+ (Deep     Premium tier unlocks,   Earned access; jackpot
  Denial)           reward content          psychology
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------

2.2 Time-of-Day Mapping

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Time Window** **Recommended Content**     **Duration**
  --------------- --------------------------- ---------------------------
  Morning (with   Short identity priming,     5-10 minutes
  coffee)         Elswyth worship (short      
                  induction)                  

  Daytime         Bambi feminization, Elswyth 20-45 minutes
  (private hours) chastity/denial, full       
                  sessions during edging      

  Evening         Elswyth sleep hypno, cuddle 15-30 minutes
  (wind-down)     sessions, chastity mantras  
                  (while caged)               
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------

2.3 Content Tiering (Ratchet Integration)

Content access is gated by protocol compliance and denial achievements,
integrating with the existing ratchet system:

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Tier**    **Access Requirement**      **Content Available**
  ----------- --------------------------- -------------------------------
  Tier 1      Daily protocol complete     Elswyth podcast (free), basic
                                          affirmations

  Tier 2      3+ day streak               Bambi core series, Elswyth
                                          chastity series

  Tier 3      7+ day streak OR denial day Premium Elswyth paid content,
              7+                          advanced Bambi

  Tier 4      Monthly milestone           Vault content, new series
                                          unlocks
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------

Part 3: Task Integration

3.1 Hypno Task Types

New task types to be added to the daily prescription system:

-   **hypno_morning** --- Short identity/worship content during morning
    protocol (5-10 min)

-   **hypno_session** --- Full feminization/conditioning session during
    private hours (20-45 min)

-   **hypno_edge** --- Content paired with edge session (duration
    matches session)

-   **hypno_sleep** --- Evening/bedtime content for overnight
    conditioning (15-30 min)

-   **hypno_caged** --- Content specifically for listening while wearing
    cage

3.2 Task Generation Logic

The AI prescription system should incorporate these factors when
generating hypno tasks:

interface HypnoTaskContext {

denialDay: number;

arousalState: \'dormant\' \| \'baseline\' \| \'elevated\' \|

\'sweet_spot\' \| \'overwhelming\' \| \'subspace\';

currentStreak: number;

isCaged: boolean;

timeOfDay: \'morning\' \| \'afternoon\' \| \'evening\' \| \'night\';

hasEdgeSessionToday: boolean;

lastHypnoCategory: string; // Avoid repetition

unlockedTier: 1 \| 2 \| 3 \| 4;

}

3.3 Weekly Task Distribution

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Task Type**       **Frequency**           **Conditions**
  ------------------- ----------------------- ---------------------------
  Morning worship     Daily (optional)        Include 3-5x per week

  Full session        2-3x per week           Denial day 3+ preferred,
  (Bambi)                                     sweet spot optimal

  Chastity            1x per week minimum     Elswyth 7 Days series,
  conditioning                                requires cage

  Sleep hypno         3x per week             Before bed, pairs well with
                                              cage

  Edge session hypno  When edge session       Sweet spot arousal state
                      scheduled               required
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------

Part 4: AI Prescription Integration

4.1 Prompt Context Extension

Add the following to the AI prescription generation context:

const hypnoContext = \`

\## Hypno Content Integration

You can prescribe hypno listening tasks. Available categories:

\- feminization (Bambi): Identity work, feminine self-concept

\- chastity (Elswyth): Denial conditioning, orgasm control

\- goddess_worship (Elswyth): Service orientation, worship rituals

\- sleep (Elswyth): Overnight conditioning, gentle reinforcement

Current user state:

\- Denial day: \${denialDay}

\- Arousal state: \${arousalState}

\- Is caged: \${isCaged}

\- Unlocked tier: \${unlockedTier}

\- Last hypno listened: \${lastHypnoCategory}

Prescription guidelines:

\- Day 0-2: Prioritize chastity/obedience content

\- Day 3-5: Mix feminization with denial reinforcement

\- Day 6+: Full feminization sessions, pair with edging

\- If caged: Include cage-specific content

\- Evening: Prefer sleep hypno for overnight conditioning

\`;

4.2 Task Output Schema

interface HypnoTask {

type: \'hypno_morning\' \| \'hypno_session\' \|

\'hypno_edge\' \| \'hypno_sleep\' \| \'hypno_caged\';

category: string;

contentId?: string; // Specific content, or null for AI selection

duration: number; // minutes

requiresCage: boolean;

pairWithEdgeSession: boolean;

description: string; // What to tell user

}

Part 5: UI Components

5.1 Component Requirements

1.  **HypnoTaskCard** --- Displays hypno task in Today view with play
    button, duration, and category indicator

2.  **HypnoContentBrowser** --- Library view showing available content
    filtered by tier/category

3.  **HypnoSessionLogger** --- Post-listen modal capturing completion
    status and effectiveness rating

4.  **HypnoStatsWidget** --- Dashboard widget showing listening hours,
    favorite categories, conditioning progress

5.  **TierUnlockModal** --- Celebration modal when new content tier is
    unlocked

5.2 File Structure

/src

/features

/hypno

/components

