HypnoContentBrowser.tsx

HypnoSessionLogger.tsx

HypnoStatsWidget.tsx

TierUnlockModal.tsx

/hooks

useHypnoContent.ts

useHypnoRecommendations.ts

useHypnoSession.ts

/lib

content-selector.ts

tier-calculator.ts

/types

hypno.ts

Part 6: Evidence & Ratchet Integration

6.1 Hypno as Evidence (Ratchet E2)

Add hypno listening stats to the evidence dashboard:

-   Total hours of conditioning listened

-   Sessions completed by category

-   Longest listening streak

-   Content tiers unlocked

-   First hypno session date (milestone marker)

6.2 Sunk Cost Integration (Ratchet H4)

Include in sunk cost dashboard display:

Conditioning received:

\- \${totalHours} hours of hypno conditioning

\- \${sessionCount} sessions completed

\- \${feminizationHours} hours of feminization

\- \${obedienceHours} hours of obedience training

Your mind has been shaped. This cannot be undone.

