Part 8: Implementation Priority

Phase 1: Foundation (Week 1)

1.  Create database schema (hypno_content, hypno_sessions)

2.  Seed initial Elswyth and Bambi content library

3.  Build useHypnoContent hook for content retrieval

4.  Build tier-calculator.ts for access logic

Phase 2: Task Integration (Week 2)

1.  Add hypno task types to prescription system

2.  Update AI prompt context with hypno guidelines

3.  Build HypnoTaskCard component

4.  Integrate into Today view

Phase 3: Logging & Evidence (Week 3)

1.  Build HypnoSessionLogger component

2.  Add hypno stats to evidence dashboard

3.  Integrate with sunk cost display

4.  Build TierUnlockModal

Phase 4: Content Browser (Week 4)

1.  Build HypnoContentBrowser component

2.  Build HypnoStatsWidget

3.  Add recommendation engine (useHypnoRecommendations)

4.  Polish and testing

Summary

This integration creates a structured audio conditioning layer that
complements the existing visual and behavioral aspects of the Becoming
Protocol. By tying content access to protocol compliance and denial
achievements, hypno listening becomes another ratchet mechanism---earned
rewards that deepen identity conditioning while making regression more
costly.

The combination of Bambi (feminization/identity) and Elswyth
(obedience/chastity/goddess worship) provides comprehensive coverage of
the psychological domains the system targets, with content
recommendations dynamically matched to the user\'s current state for
maximum conditioning effectiveness.
